{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-readme-js","path":"/willianjusten/awesome-svg/readme/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"77531cf1-4489-54ab-ba2b-a380c7744e4c","html":"<img src=\"https://rawgit.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/master/logo.svg\" alt=\"Awesome SVG\">\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\"><img src=\"https://cdn.rawgit.com/sindresorhus/awesome/d7305f38d29fed78fa85652e3a63e154dd8e8829/media/badge.svg\" alt=\"Awesome\"></a> <a href=\"https://travis-ci.org/willianjusten/awesome-svg\"><img src=\"https://travis-ci.org/willianjusten/awesome-svg.svg?branch=master\" alt=\"Travis Build\"></a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>A curated list of SVG. The main idea is that everyone can contribute here, so we can center all the informations about SVG and keep up-to-date.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#awesome-svg\">Awesome SVG</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/blob/master/topics/Accessibility.md\">Accessible SVG</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/blob/master/topics/Animation.md\">Animation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/blob/master/topics/Books.md\">Books</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/blob/master/topics/Experiments.md\">Experiments</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/blob/master/topics/Filters.md\">Filters</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/blob/master/topics/Follow-twitter.md\">Follow on Twitter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/blob/master/topics/Gradients.md\">Gradients</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/blob/master/topics/Grunt-plugins.md\">Grunt Plugins</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/blob/master/topics/Gulp-plugins.md\">Gulp Plugins</a></li>\n<li><