\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Thanks to...</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mvfsillva\">Marcus Vinicius</a>, my friend =)</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/rcmachado\">Rodrigo Machado</a> for helping me with CC License.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Cleysonlb\">Cleyson Leal</a> for creating the awesome logo.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://chriscoyier.net/\">Chris Coyier</a> and his <a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/mega-list-svg-information/\">Compendium of SVG Information</a>, was a great start point for me.</li>\n<li>and of course, all the <a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/graphs/contributors\">Contributors</a>.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"contributing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contributing\" aria-label=\"contributing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contributing</h2>\n<p>Your contributions are always welcome! <a href=\"https://github.com/willianjusten/awesome-svg/blob/master/contributing.md\">Click Here to read the guidelines</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"other-awesome-lists\" style=\"positio